        <mxCell id="cTS2Bc4Euz190X_VzW5h-157" value="Ū&lt;sub&gt;c&lt;/sub&gt;(q) = f(α, β, Ū&lt;sub&gt;c,11&lt;/sub&gt;, Ū&lt;sub&gt;c,12&lt;/sub&gt;, Ū&lt;sub&gt;c,21&lt;/sub&gt;, Ū&lt;sub&gt;c,22&lt;/sub&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The local flow velocity is obtained by a weighted average of the four surrounding grid-point velocities based on α and β." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;strokeColor=#2E7D32;strokeWidth=2;fontFamily=Times New Roman;fontSize=16;fillColor=#FFFFFF;" vertex="1" parent="1">
